# reflector

> Arch script to fetch and sort mirrorlists
> More information: https://manned.org/reflector

- Get all mirrors, sort for download speed and save them:

`sudo reflector --sort {string value: rate} --save {string value: /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist}`

- Only get German HTTPS mirrors:

`reflector --country {string value: Germany} --protocol {string value: https}`

- Only get the 10 recently sync'd mirrors:

`reflector --latest {int value: 10}`
